{"tid":588444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(截止下午三時半)  各區投票率","createTime":"2018-03-11T08:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T08:32:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9197e2adc28da03d2d92b0f657ff43c0eea76fd4","tid":588444,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T08:21:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=997025&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D997025%26csid%3D261_341&d=wIsT1otLT%2FLa6DRoCHtl%2F57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=cdf9059a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=997025&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會補選，截止下午三時半，有超過45萬7千人參與香港島、九龍西及新界東地方選區投票，投票率是21.78%。<br />\n<br />\n三區投票率分別是：<br />\n<br />\n香港島22.55%； 2016年換屆時是27.98%<br />\n<br />\n九龍西23.35%；2016年換屆時是27.69%<br />\n<br />\n新界東20.52%；2016年換屆時是27.17%<br />\n<br />\n至於建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界功能組別補選，有超過2千7百人投票，投票率36.72%，較前年換屆選舉同一時段高2.74個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20180311_20180311-154831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20180311_20180311-154831.jpg&h=62f2f3fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b19de7c10c9b2ba467f902384978fdab7e18c18e","tid":588444,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T08:27:08.000Z","msg":"新界東巴打真係唔去含撚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d14484a5d65dfea18509e457509339bf341840","tid":588444,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T08:32:48.000Z","msg":"新界東選民真係好高質！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}